positive.review:
Man I can't get enough of this game! Think of Project Zomboid, Diablo and DayZ; this game is somewhere in between. 
Here are some of the things that I can think of:
- Good gameplay and combat (could be better, but I hear they are working on it);
- Nice weapon and vehicle customization (you also have horses!!!);
- Clothes could be better, like, in a greater number and variety (what we have till now is good enough though);
- It has seasons, each with its own challenges and visual style;
- You can construct your own home, or can upgrade an existing one (there are also bunkers for those apocalypse fan boys and preppers);
- There are also human enemies, small and big game, zombified animals also;
- You get quests and most of them are ok (except maybe the one, where some doctor has to follow you and he is brain dead, to be elegant at most)- this can be better;
- and a lot of other things that are in the game and a lot more to come, judging by the fact that the devs are very active and hard working.
So mates, you be wrong when buying this, it's awesome!

